lead_paragraph: MURPHY--Edmund, May 1, 1930, died July 3, 2016. Beloved husband of Virginia, father of Anne, Edmund, Mary, Thomas, Brian, Ellen, Joseph, and Kevin. Grandfather of 20. Great-grandfather of five. Services, 10am, Wednesday, St. Agnes. 1/3
